Q: How does attachment to joy from thoughts or prayers become transformed to tranquility?
<br>A: What is the experience?
<br>Q: Joy.
<br>A: Peace.
<br>Q: But there is still excitement.
<br>A: It is not joy then. There is some pleasure.
<br>Q: How to transform that to tranquility?
<br>A: By regular practice of meditation. <span class=date>1/9/97</span>
